#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:53
msgid "``allUsers``"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:55
msgid ""
"Boolean. If set to ``false``, :pipeline:`$currentOp` will only report "
"operations belonging to the user who ran the command. If set to ``true``,"
" :pipeline:`$currentOp` will report operations belonging to all users."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:62
msgid ""
"The ``inprog`` privilege is necessary to run :pipeline:`$currentOp` with "
"``{ allUsers : true }``."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:65
#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:72
msgid "Defaults to ``false``."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:67
msgid "``idleConnections``"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:68
msgid ""
"Boolean. If set to ``false``, :pipeline:`$currentOp` will only report "
"active operations. If set to ``true``, all operations including idle "
"connections will be returned."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:75
msgid "Constraints"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:77
msgid ":pipeline:`$currentOp` must be the first stage in the pipeline."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:79
msgid ""
"Pipelines that start with :pipeline:`$currentOp` can only be run on the "
"``admin`` database."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:82
msgid ""
"On a standalone or replica set with authentication enabled, the "
"``inprog`` privilege is required to run :pipeline:`$currentOp` if the "
"``allUsers`` parameter is set to `true`."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/aggregation/currentOp.txt:86
msgid ""
"On a sharded cluster, the ``inprog`` privilege is required to run all "
":pipeline:`$currentOp` pipelines."
msgstr ""

